{"tid":15500,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯想以破紀錄天價買尼馬","createTime":"2016-12-01T04:18:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T05:41:37.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"267d02b89d53b87d69f89dca3be02a73d5e7f654","tid":15500,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:18:59.000Z","msg":"《Daily Record》報道，曼聯或重燃對巴塞隆拿前鋒尼馬的興趣，但要把他簽入，相信需要非常天價。<br />\n<br />\n消息指如果尼馬表明想他投，「紅魔鬼」就會考慮出手，價錢應該會比簽下普巴的8500萬鎊世界紀錄轉會費更高。<br />\n<br />\n特別是尼馬10月時才簽新合約，如果曼聯想將這位巴西球星收歸旗下，相信巴塞要高達1億8000萬鎊才肯放人。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=5e7fe23a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"229e2fecb8806f759ed78b6090a67ca2dea422ee","tid":15500,"uid":4082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:31:55.000Z","msg":"曼聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c22a8441386c667061d8eb9da92c4791173df4be","tid":15500,"uid":12547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:33:32.000Z","msg":"牙朗筆錢真係襟洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6470cfe625654b2ff4ce1b30f812b0fd0c154f9","tid":15500,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:34:18.000Z","msg":"買啦！<br />\n削弱巴，無助曼，廢尼馬<br />\n三贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100fd613a9e2b0e43d27d807810877003eec870a","tid":15500,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:36:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買啦！<br />\n削弱巴，無助曼，廢尼馬<br />\n三贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買走尼馬邊個最開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f0e91fda13add7a4a3995088505dcf7171180e","tid":15500,"uid":45428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:41:45.000Z","m